<title>
CVT Fluid Cooler Hose Replacement
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5506032">CVT Fluid Cooler Hose Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Rubber hoses for CVT fluid cooler should be checked at specified interval. If replacing them, be sure to note the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Remove front bumper lower absorber, if necessary. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9806002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Remove left side engine undercover, if necessary.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Replace clamps with new ones at the same time.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Clamp clamps securely.
</ptxt>
